徑、目標器官等），並提出具體的飲食建議或加工改良方法，以降低消費
者攝入這些有害物質的風險。（25 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:38:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "e67cbfb8ed4f", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "114040", "c": "412", "s": "2008", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "食品衛生與安全概要", "year": "114", "exam_name": "114年公務人員特種考試關務人員考試、身心障礙人員考試、國軍上校以上軍官轉任公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "三", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "disabled", "civil_category": "衛生技術"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('disabled-704caaf1-moex-00042', 'disabled-704caaf1', 'disabled-704caaf1-moex-114-6cba014f', 'sub-disabled-704caaf1-04', NULL, 'essay', '請依「農場至餐桌」（FromFarmtoTable）的概念，分析食品生產鏈中的
